data.description: Assumable loan at 2.75%!  Wonderfully maintained 3 bedroom ranch.  Updated kitchen with SS appliances, granite countertops, pantry, and large island.  Split bedroom floorplan with a spacious primary suite including customized walk-in closet.  Don't miss the newly remodeled walk-out basement including a large rec room with wet bar,  3/4 bath area, and generous storage room.  Enjoy the  outdoors on the large deck and fenced backyard.  This home offers a newer roof (2021), water heater (2021), and remodeled main bath area.  Amenities such as restaurants, shopping, and schools are only minutes away.
